column3: “This is amazing bud. It's high in THC, but does not cause any paranoia and it also leaves me clear headed; so, I can focus- instead of sitting around with couch-lock and memory loss.... Helps my pain in my lower back and neck dissappear. I am very happy and satisfied with this strain. A+++++”

“Minutes after medicating with this strain, all of my back pain disappeared. Hybrid quality good for after work medicating. This one will put you to sleep if you arent careful. I was overly satisfied with the medicinal qualitiy of this strain, however, I was unimpressed with the aesthetic properties that this strain posses.”
“This strain is the truth. Very good taste and powerful strong. A must try for smokers who enjoy good strong cannabis.”
“Definitely an indica... But great bedtime high... Giggles, relaxed. Smooth sleep transition. Dense bud... Will get again.”
“Straight fuego! Diesel tested at 27% THC 🤘”

“I absolutely love the taste of this strain in concentrate form! But I never buy something for the flavor...so here's the 818 OG (Not to be confused with SFV OG I believe)
After my 2nd dab I started feeling my body relax from toe to head. Which was unique since I usually first feel relaxation toward top of my body then the relaxation moves downward.
Very rarely do I get hungry. I actually forget to eat a lot. Can't go...”

“Hard hitting, great pine taste. Couch lock on this one, great buy.
Very Dank.”
“Overall very good little harsh but tasty”
“my favorite by far!! live this strain”

“one of a kind smoke
ive had it twice about a year apart. kaleafa in portland test at 27% 
its different..... must try”
“flavor wasnt incredible but this is a great strain for insomnia and pain. definitely knocked me out!”
“Overall very good little harsh but tasty”
“omg!! the best flavor, feeling I have ever had!!”

“I can’t stop buying this strain. I get along really well with the terpenes. I’ve been smoking for over 10 years and 818 is my go-to sleep aid strain. Knocks me OUT. Really helps with anxiety and pain. Panic attack stopper!”

“I love this strain! Both flower and shatter, the awesome bud tender turned me on to it. This flower takes all my pain away and it makes my mind tingle😍 It remains on my shopping list when my store has it.”
“Super relaxing and long lasting....this is one of those strains you watch a semi rated comedy and laugh your ass off anyway.  You will feel sluggish is smoked a lot but still well worth it.”
“very good weed!”
“Definitely one of my favorite strains so far. You get lost in this high. Extremely uplifting. Very giggly when you aren't lost.”
“the best so far!! super duper snoney”
“fire”

“I've only seen this cut once and it was the Vicks vapor rub pheno,not as describe by Queafly.  

Who knows, but I love that Vicks..”
“Top 10 for chronic pain relief.”

“Couch LOCK.. I am a picky man and this Firebrand 818 OG is powerful. You will have severe rubber neck and that means.. even with an epic tolerance this will leave you amazed. Left this review because I went back 2 days later to buy more and this flower is worth leaving a review.”

“One of my favorites, next to L.S.D..  Thi bud never seems to fail or live up to its name.  This is one of those strains (or so it seems), that if it hasn't been flushed (burn grey/black), had mold, was harvested to early = racy, it never seems to matter, popcorn​ shrimp size buds to big apple size buds, it always seems to smoke the same.  This must be one of those strains that just stays the same no matter what.  If ...”
“I was not hot on this strain I am a heavy smoker and it did nothing for me witch was a dissipointment because I love the OG strains .”
“I have a half ounce of this”
